title: Air ambulance called to accident in Cornwall | West Country (W)
text:
The B3314 is closed in both directions due to a serious accident around Menefreda Way in St Minver.
Police and an air ambulance are at the scene.
Officers say the road is likely to remain closed into the night.
Last updated Wed 23 Sep 2015 Travel St Minver Cornwall and Isles of Scilly
